<p><a href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2023/03/08/really-just-one-color-and-its-yellow" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Speaking of Playdate</a>, Panic has news:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Arriving with the latest Playdate OS and also available at
<a href="https://play.date/games" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">play.date/games</a>, Catalog is our curated store for neat
